  Copa Nordeste 1999
u 2nd leg Oct 19
v 2nd leg Oct 21
w 2nd leg Oct 19; San Lorenzo replace Sol de América who withdrew
x Talleres replace Gimnasia y Esgrima (La Plata) who withdrew
y 1st leg Oct 12; Deportes Concepción replace Cobreloa who withdrew
z both teams withdrew 

